source: hand-authored
capture_date: 2026-07-05
gitlab_version: 17.x
endpoint: GET /projects/:id/issues/:iid/resource_label_events
shape: label event array with add/remove actions; leaf filters action=="add" AND label.name==LABEL.
notes: |
  Multiple `add` events for the same label — the leaf returns the NEWEST
  matching created_at.
